{"tid":191302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做炒散狗真係慘撚過乞丐","createTime":"2017-04-07T18:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T03:58:37.000Z","uid":33375,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"718647078cafa7e28ce53fdeff148bef8c256e61","tid":191302,"uid":33375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:11:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的，上年我就返過Rugby7既炒散，係跟Holidxx Ixx既，咁上年都好地地。今年有條友打黎問我今年仲返唔返，咁我見做啲野又唔辛苦，又可以免費睇波，咁咪話返，比哂啲個人資料佢，銀行都比埋。<br />\n跟住一開始仲問條撚樣我有Fd都想返佢仲請唔請，佢仲話幾多都請。咁佢之後開左個group，之前仲話入左個群組就無問題。<br />\n咁Rubgy7就係4月7，8，9號啦，佢話4月1號要去briefing，咁我都有去。佢仲比哂當日返工既資料我地。<br />\n點撚知，臨開工前兩日佢無撚啦啦腥個whatsapp黎話今年人數full撚左，下年再黎。跟住就開始好多人係個group屌哂老母，相信被放飛機嘅有過兩百人。<br />\n好明顯係一開始班撚樣驚唔夠人，係咁請，點知而家又太多，我屌你老母咩淨係打你一份工咩？推撚哂啲job預返工點撚知比人放飛機。可想而知，炒散狗真係一文不值，你只係一個工具。<br />\n真心唔撚明點解間大公司會請班on9既黎做supervisor，分配人手又唔識，仲話自己讀緊書，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟有無巴絲都係受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/021127_d6ca24d1cdade600527cf4842ec50a33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F021127_d6ca24d1cdade600527cf4842ec50a33.jpg&h=226ee025&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/021127_f81051afacf2dfe07e36dadd3747343d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F021127_f81051afacf2dfe07e36dadd3747343d.jpg&h=49971c86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af9082a1e7a800fcc04d1aa9587e4afc1ddae784","tid":191302,"uid":86311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18:14:00.000Z","msg":"係慘既"},{"pid":"0667aef6629e59e7a194c56f99d7fccccee88977","tid":191302,"uid":33375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T18